11月后抗争形式急剧恶化，今天理工大学被围攻，支援的医务人员、报道真相的记者等无关人员都被逮捕，校内学生进退维谷，感觉六四的悲剧在一步步靠近，心如刀割。我能想到的能做的事情，就是用英文向自由世界发声。发推，ping议员，推动S.1838在参议院尽早过关。有心相助的手足们一起动动手指，再小的力量也是支持，救港人也是救我们自己。<br>
<br>
我提供一个自己写的模版（英语水平有限），英语好的手足也请帮忙提供模版：<br>
A humanitarian tragedy is happening in Hong Kong Polytechnic University. HK policies surrounded the campus and are now arresting medical workers and journalists who are going to help the protesting students, which is illegal even in a war. Things waiting for the protesting students are either dead in the campus or arrested and treated by terror just like the increasing hundreds of unnatural deaths and sexual abuses in HK in the past several months. Senator, please pass S.1838 “The Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act of 2019” as soon as possible!<br>
<br>
